==Recognition==
Smith is ranked #8 on &quot;Total Guitar&#x27;s&quot; list of the Greatest Metal Guitarists of All Time, #28 on &quot;Loudwire&#x27;s&quot; Best 75 Hard Rock/Metal Guitarists of All Time, and also takes 11th place in the list of the 100 greatest metal guitarists of all time according to &quot;Guitar World&quot; magazine together with Dave Murray and 4th place together with Dave Murray and Janick Gers (all three are Iron Maiden guitarists ) – in the list of the greatest metal guitarists of all time according to &quot;Metal Hammer&quot;. Also he is ranked jointly with Dave Murray at number 83 on &quot;Rolling Stone&#x27;s&quot; list of the 250 Greatest Guitarists of All Time.

